== Availability ==
The Zephyrus is only available at the [[OTAS Shipyard]] in [[Legend's Home]].  For such an effective ship, however, it is quite cheap.

== Suggested Roles==
Thanks in large part to its speed and armament, a Zephyrus makes a good escort for standard freighters.  Its respectable cargo capacity enables it to act as a transport ship quite effectively, though admittedly it has the smallest cargo bay of the TM class.
